OL,3,CNurses on strike over 'fire and
OL,4,Crehire' contract changes
OL,6,FNurses are striking against contract
OL,7,Fchanges that would see shifts shared
OL,8,Fout over Bassetlaw and Doncaster
OL,9,Fhospitals.
OL,11,FFrom Monday 15 December until Friday
OL,12,F19 December, nurses from the intensive
OL,13,Fcare unit at Bassetlaw Hospital are
OL,14,Fstriking to try and prevent contract
OL,15,Fchanges.
OL,17,FIf the changes go ahead, the nurses
OL,18,Fwill be forced to rotate between the
OL,19,Fhospitals in Bassetlaw and Doncaster.
