OL,3,CNurses on strike over 'fire and
OL,4,Crehire' contract changes
OL,6,FAccording to the Unite union, nurses
OL,7,Ffear the transfers are one step
OL,8,Ftowards Bassetlaw Hospital losing its
OL,9,FICU permanently.
OL,11,FWith the two hospitals nearly 19 miles
OL,12,Fapart, nurses would also face longer
OL,13,Fcommutes before and after 13-hour
OL,14,Fshifts.
OL,16,FFran Taylor has worked at Bassetlaw
OL,17,FHospital for 32 years on the ICU.
