OL,6,FShe said: "Personally I don't drive so
OL,7,Ffor me it's pretty much and two and
OL,8,Fhalf hour round trip on public
OL,9,Ftransport and I couldn't get there for
OL,10,Fthe shift times.
OL,12,F"I don't know what I'll do to be
OL,13,Fhonest. I don't know what I will do. I
OL,14,Fdon't want to be forced out because of
OL,15,Fthis."
