OL,3,CNurses on strike over 'fire and
OL,4,Crehire' contract changes
OL,6,FUnite regional officer Chris Rawlinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "What the trust said at the
OL,8,Fopening meetings for these proposals
OL,9,Fis that eventually Bassetlaw ICU will
OL,10,Fnot have any permanent staff and will
OL,11,Finstead be staffed by nurses on
OL,12,Frotation from Doncaster.
OL,14,F"If you don't have permanent staff
OL,15,Fworking on this unit then you have
OL,16,Fpeople who aren't used to the unit and
OL,17,Fwhere things are and that puts people
OL,18,Fat risk."
