OL,3,CNurses on strike over 'fire and
OL,4,Crehire' contract changes
OL,6,FThe trust claims rotating shifts will
OL,7,Fincrease the nurses' exposure to level
OL,8,Fthree patients, and therefore lead to
OL,9,Fupskilling.
OL,11,FMs Taylor said: "We have had level 3,
OL,12,Fthat's ventilated patients, virtually
OL,13,Fevery week for the last four or five
OL,14,Fweeks so we get plenty of exposure to
OL,15,Flevel three patients. Most of us are
OL,16,Fvery experienced nurses and we have
OL,17,Fbeen looking after critically ill
OL,18,Fpatients for years."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
