OL,3,CNurses on strike over 'fire and
OL,4,Crehire' contract changes
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "The trust's abhorrent fire and
OL,8,Frehire threats have only made the
OL,9,Fnurses more determined to fight
OL,10,Fagainst this blatant attempt to run
OL,11,Fdown Bassetlaw's ICU. They have
OL,12,FUnite's 100% support in standing up
OL,13,Ffor themselves and patients."
OL,15,FMr Rawlinson said: "Unite offered the
OL,16,Ftrust a cost-neutral plan that would
OL,17,Fgive nurses more level 3 experience.
OL,18,FIts rejection of the plan shows the
OL,19,Freal aim: the decommissioning by
OL,20,Fstealth of Bassetlaw's ICU.
