OL,6,F"Our members don't want to strike, but
OL,7,Fthey can't accept proposals that
OL,8,Fundermine patient care and force
OL,9,Funreasonable commute times on top of
OL,10,F13-hour shifts."
OL,12,FIn response, the Bassetlaw and
OL,13,FDoncaster Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust said: "Our priority
OL,15,Fis patient safety and that means our
OL,16,Fhighly skilled ICU nurses maintain the
OL,17,Flevel of competency our critically ill
OL,18,Fpatients rightly expect.
